9套。由于游戏支持免费的次世代升级，因此应该有不少精明的玩家会选择购买PS4版的《最终幻想7重制版》二手盘来进行升级。另外一款PS5新作《瑞奇与叮当：时空跳转》的销量也只有14663套。相比之下，同一款游戏的NS版本要比PS版本高上数倍。当然一部分原因也是PS5在日本已经售罄，硬件并不容易买到。实际上不仅是日本，PS5目前在全球范围内都是缺货状态。日本现在的PS5安装基数接近100万台，主机很可能被黄牛或奸商等转运到亚洲其他地区，PS5游戏的销量也势必会受到影响，毕竟没有主机买来游戏也没什么用。PS5游戏在日本销量不佳！同一款游戏NS销量是PS数倍"},"attached_info":"Cj4I0J/W2+76oPMgEAMaCDY1OTUzMjc0IP/xxYYGMAY4UUAecgk0NjY1MzE0NzN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"119 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f29bbcb09d72519b52f1ae2822682800_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"31_1624507702.8442397","card_id":"Q_362989562","target":{"id":362989562,"title":"你有哪些提升自我的好习惯？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/362989562","type":"question","created":1577290652,"answer_count":1798,"follower_count":25720,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[800,40758,70523],"comment_count":12,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAI0J/W2+76oPMgEAMaCDQyOTQzMjk5IJyXjvAFMAw4+MgBQB9yCTM2Mjk4OTU2MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"105 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-365d3ab2b86a201da0f6d0c8fb4b4a43_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"32_1624507702.8446527","card_id":"Q_328517811","target":{"id":328517811,"title":"刚参加完高考，下一步报什么专业就业率高？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/328517811","type":"question","created":1560058213,"answer_count":43,"follower_count":96,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3392,5830,42019],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"大学毕业以后就业率的问题。 本提问已被收录进「志愿选择题」活动中。这个 6 月，贡献 >100 字的优质回答，参与瓜分 10,000 现金。还有机会解锁「高考答疑官」认证资格，期待看到你的回答。 活动详情见：志愿选择题｜2021